flowRoot.flowPara: Embracing and leveraging modern technology and practices provides the highest quality and most cost-effective products and services to employees, citizens and businesses.
Proactively educating staff is critical to realizing the potential of modern tools and methods.

We believe in individuals and interactions over processes and tools, working solutions over comprehensive documentation, collaboration over contract negotiation, and responding to change over following a plan.
While we value the latter, we value the former more.
Employees should be able to access what they need to work from any location and on any platform.
Usability is a critical component of accessibility and user experience design should be an integral part of every new or upgraded system.
Governance of the Information, Platform, and Presentation layers provides consistency for employees and citizens and reduces costs through economies of scale and collaborative funding.
The most important contributor to successful governance is providing compelling products and services.

We believe in the power of open data and API’s to provide government transparency and leverage the creativity of employees and citizens, the power of open standards to ensure flexibility and interoperability in our solutions, and that open source software should be on equal footing with proprietary software in the enterprise.
